Currently v-model only works on native form elements (`<input>`, `<textarea>`, `<select>`).
Component v-model is explicitly rejected with \"not supported yet\".

## Expected

```html
<MyInput v-model='name' />
```

Should desugar to `:modelValue='name.get()'` + `@update:modelValue='name.set'` prop/emit pair, consistent with Vue 3 component v-model convention.